{
  "stem": "151.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- we went back and we found out accidentally that my father-- somebody saw my father in Theresienstadt in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we decided to go back to Prague and go to Terezin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We needed-- we found out that there may be a chance that it's him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so my husband was look-- my brother was looking for a truck that if we find him we should be able to bring him from Terezin to Prague, to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And again accidentally we ran into my husband, Bernard, who was in the forced labor camp with my brother earlier.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they embraced and were very pleased to see each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my husband, he had access to an UNRRA truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they went to Theresienstadt and went into a room where my father's name was on the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my brother went from bed to bed searching for my father and couldn't find him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he came back again, looked at the list and sure enough my father's name was there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he went back again and again he couldn't find him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as he was walking out somebody called his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he turned back and he said he faced this skeleton of a man [PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] who was dying of tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They brought him to Prague.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We took them to a very famous tuberculosis sanatorium called [INAUDIBLE] and a few months later my father died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before he died, he told us a very interesting story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He asked my brother whether on a certain date whether he escaped from the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, my brother told him that he escaped, and my father said was it on such and such day?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
